properties.description: This pipeline will load table AIA_IMS_POLICY_DETAILS_STG on Every Week Monday 11:00 AM

source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT *

  FROM [AIA_102].AIA_IMS_BOB_WEEKLY_DATA_LOADS_CONSOLIDATION 

   WHERE AIA_102.AIA_IMS_BOB_WEEKLY_DATA_LOADS_CONSOLIDATION.Policy_ID NOT IN (SELECT 

      AIA_102.AIA_BOB_ALL_AGENCY_ALL_POLICY_ALL_TRANSACTION_ID_HISTORY.Policy_ID

        FROM [AIA_102].[AIA_BOB_ALL_AGENCY_ALL_POLICY_ALL_TRANSACTION_ID_HISTORY] );
